Fire story:
The innovator IBM is into the second century of its existence
If you are looking for a suitable word that the strategy of IBM most accurate, it would be the word 'longevity. "
For the general public is IBM a synonym for technological revolution, it is known as a modern businesses, although since its inception a century has passed.
The basis for this longevity has presented its first chief - the visionary Thomas J. Watson first
He was already the slogan, countless global problems could be solved easily if people were prepared to consider a bit.
His slogan: "Think!" Was the trademark to the life of the future giants (and, at the same time, the title of the corporate internal magazine with IBM already publish began in 1935).
This was also the basis of Watsen thoroughly prepared corporate culture.
"For us from IBM means this long-term thinking a kontinuelle movement towards the future.
IBM survived and was also an entire century successful because it has remained true to its principles and not shied away from using everything surrounding it.
This allowed us, in the course of our first century, the technologies, the Business and also to transform society.
We hope that the next hundred years to create even more, "said Samuel J. Palmisano, the current director of the company on the occasion of the anniversary.
Thought-out system
Watson has been carried out in the 1930s social care of its employees, in a similar way, such as entrepreneurs Baťa in Czechoslovakia: The IBM people had to be one of the first American workers paid leave, an insurance through employers plus elegant uniforms and work clothes and a reasonable remuneration system for best innovators and traders.
As more sophisticated, the long-term relationships with customers by IBM.
The company was brilliant in the talent promotion - as one of the first companies worldwide, IBM any discrimination - and could choose accordingly.
