Not surprisingly, there is no shortage of ideas, the company is almost half a million people.
An institution with a good reputation
Their unshakeable position in the business for the company and a strong image at home and abroad.
"From the beginning, IBM was the concept of an institution rather than a mere technology company," said Economist the professor at Harvard Business School and the author of a book on IBM, Rosabeth Moss Kanter.
"IBM is not a technology company, but a firm, the business through technology helps solve problems," added George Colony of Consulting-firm Forrester Research.
As the company itself points out, there is a difference in the market to be present only by the presence or him directly.
IBM - in the states of their logos for family "Big Blue", in a century, is one of the largest companies in the world has come of age.
It is one of the most diverse technology companies have developed - IBM hardware and software, infrastructure, hosting and consulting services in an incredible product broad - from servers to nanotechnology.
Of all the American technology companies, IBM most patents and five of its staff were awarded the Nobel Prize.
His most famous inventions include, for example, bank machines, credit cards, financial swaps, bar code or the diskette.
With approximately $220 billion in stock market value (market capitalization) was IBM this year, the second-largest technology companies (after Apple), and for the first time since 1996 Microsoft obsolete.
Looking ahead
Not all products and innovations, the taste of the customers of today - for example, the attempt was unhappy with its own operating system, os/2, the online service Prodigy or the computer IBM PC Jr.
"Business is based on the forward movement, so we should not emotionell tied to the past," says to Samuel J. Palmisano.
