In these investment drive IBM after 2008, when the latter-day financial crisis for the first time as a storm swept across the world.
Here, too, IBM was the legacy of his first boss Thomas J. Watson faithful, in the middle of a major global economic crisis his investment volume increased.
So far, it appears that the company IBM emerges unscathed from the current crisis.
The value of the IBM shares rose raketenartig since 2008 by 120 percent and net profit of the company is growing kontinuell.
The company slogan of IBM is: Everything can change not only the values.
It is also expected that this flexible giant pulls off the next crisis.
IBM history: The cheese Schneider to outer space flights
The one hundred years ago in New York-based company IBM (International Business Machines) was initially a very complicated name - Computing Tabulating recording Corporation.
The name IBM took until 1924 - it was originally a brand name for a branch in Canada and South America.
The foundation for later society IBM, the merger of four companies, whose history until the 1980s, dating back to the 19th century.
They owned technologies such as the famous Stechkartenuhren on registration of work and endes begins.
The architects of this new company was Charles Ranlett Flint, until 1930 also holds the presidency of the supervisory board.
And it was Flint, the head of the rival firm Thomas J. Watson hit for him in the management of the company.
This Leader, then even the founder of IBM in the shadow - based on Watson's ideas until today the unbesiegbare culture and identity of the company.
Watson led the company until 1952.
IBM, began, as the name suggests, with the production and distribution of all sorts of machinery for trade - of sausage-and Käseschneidern to cash.
In the first four decades in which Watson the company, he has doubled its sales to nine million dollars and the company, finance and on all continents.
Watson was so essential to the company that he whole forty years head sat in the chair, he was only by his son, Thomas Watson junior.
IBM began under his leadership in the development of artificial intelligence work and developed the first Programmiersprache.
In the 1960s helped engineers and computer from IBM NASA flights into space over the Merkur and Saturn, and in 1969, the famous flight of people to the moon.
Meanwhile, IBM in 1964, the first computer family with the same computer architecture - the number of IBM System/360.
A classic PC, the computer-standard that time certain, came in 1981 under the name of IBM 5150 onto the market.
Twenty years later veräußerte IBM his computer production to the Chinese company Lenovo, on the other hand, however, they bought the consul aunts part of the firm PricewaterhouseCoopers and rose to fully in the business with Consultingleistungen and services with high added value.
The strategy, IBM in the last three years, pays is the concept of "smarter planet".
It is the intention of technologies to clever way has not even planned areas, for example, to improve the situation in the transport and in the cities of administration.
IBM recently in the trade sector led the platform "smarter Commerce", which is intended to help the dealers, the whole of the business cycle.
IBM also has a strong history in the Czech Republic.
In 1932, IBM founded a branch in the former Czechoslovakia at all - the first country in Central and Eastern Europe.
Today, IBM ČR, among other things, a strategic outsourcing Center in Brno.
The Centre for Central and Eastern Europe take up residence in Prague and there is also a top research team of world-class that with the technology of Stimmerkennung.
