As we revealed a lie
A look at the current headlines shows how serious and widespread deception and lies in their daily lives.
The Republican presidential candidate, Herman Cain, is concerned with the allegations of sexual harassment on the part of several women. Both sides accuse each other of lying.
The leadership of Penh State is accused of my EID's, because it has withheld allegedly reports, after which a retired football coach sexually abused boys.
