Monti has succeeded in less than three days to form a government, which is much less time than normal. Meanwhile, Italy is fighting against the political and financial crisis, the cost of debt in an intolerable level.
The new, the former EU Commissioner Monti-led government needs to adopt a tough austerity package by the euro was called for politicians to regain the confidence in Italy.
