MSS announces a research protocol to the discovery of the gene for obesity in
The Social Security Institution of Mexico is leading a research project for the location of the gene for obesity in children and young people, which is supported by specialists of the IPN.
The Instituto Mexicano del Seguro Social - Mexico's Social Security Institute (IMSS) announced that it is a research project to the discovery of the gene for obesity in children and adolescents under the title "genetics of obesity in childhood and youth", with the genetic markers associated with obesity are to be found.
Miguel Cruz López, head of the Unidad de Investigación Médica en Bioquímica (Department for medical research, focus biochemistry) at the clinic Hospital de Especialidades del Centro regions Médico Nacional Siglo XXI said that an interdisciplinary team composed of doctors, Krankenpflegern, nutrition specialists and social workers was built.
This team will be supported by specialists and students of Postgraduiertenstudiengangs at the Instituto Nacional de Salud pública (INSP) and the Centro regions de Investigación y de Estudios Avanzados (Cinvestav) del Instituto Politécnico Nacional (IPN).
The public is invited to participate in the study, interested parties can on sports fields of IMSS in the valley of Mexico, where every Saturday from 8 a.m. tests with children and young people.
He stressed that the investigation at the sports ground of Cuauhtémoc (in the west of the state of México) began and since 8 October at the sports ground of Nezahualcóyolt (in the east of the state of México) will continue.
If the aim of 500 to 600 persons inquiry is achieved, the study on the sports ground of Independencia (in the south of the main town of Districts) and continued in Morelos (in the north of the main city Districts) completed.
He said that the aim of the study was the understanding of the factors and the role of genetics in connection with the development of obesity and the identification of risk factors of Mexican children and young people on the prevention of chronic degenerative diseases.
On the occasion of the global day of diabetes, he said it would seek that three thousand children and adolescents aged six to 14 years, with the consent and under the supervision of their parents nutritional fill out questionnaires.
You will also be questions about their physical activity and their family disease in history to risk factors that lead to diabetes and renal insufficiency may have to control.
He also led to the investigation of the aforementioned Saturdays persons measured (weight, height, Taillenumfang) to control their blood pressure and blood values such as glucose levels, Triglyceride, Cholesterol, insulin and genetic factors (attempt to identify genes associated with childhood obesity).
Cruz López said, this would take place at the concern of health staff about the alarming weight gain of young people.
"The health surveys from 1999 and 2006 showed that in less than six years, the proportion of obese boys to 77 per cent and the girls with obesity increased by 47%. The obesity has risen dramatically," said the specialist of the IMSS.
He stated that the search for genetic markers was justified because the genetic history of the population of Mexico from the other international differences.
He stated that a (e) (in) on average 65 per cent indianisch-American, European and 30% to 5% of African descent, which is in the genes, with diabetes and obesity, '.
More generally, he said the genetics of obesity in the inability to express the surplus of detainees to burn energy (calories), so that it will be stored in the form of fat.
The researchers said that the direct benefit for the study participants would be in a comprehensive study of children, were found, whether such a degree of obesity and obesity.
It would even the presence in the neck and dark Hautfalten Innenarm (Akanthosis) on the likelihood of metabolism disorders and diabetes at the preliminary stage, investigated.
All information will be treated as confidential and parents in writing of the doctors told the doctors say parents beat them all measurements and lifestyle changes that are appropriate for the prevention of diseases.
Cruz López said that there would be three basic factors for being overweight, obesity and other chronic diseases are responsible, lack of exercise, the lack of movement in everyday life, for most of the day in front of the television and transport to spend, rather than short track walking.
The high caloric intake, which means that an increased consumption of gezuckerten drinks and total carbohydrate content (Tamales, bread, pizza, hamburgers, etc.), together with a high fat and protein intake and genetics in this research project is to be analysed.
Asphalt of the UNAM prevented blow holes
Rafael Herrera, researchers at the School of Chemistry at the Mexican university UNAM developed with Polymeren modified Asphalte resilient to the mix of weather conditions and temperature fluctuations
Would the signs that the effective, respected, it would not be necessary, nearly 200,000 blow holes to repair when the rainy season in the Zona Metropolitana del Valle de México (city area of the valley of Mexico), said Rafael Herrera Nájera, researchers at the School of Chemistry (FQ) at the University of UNAM, warning and assured that if the laying and maintenance of Asphaltbelags if appropriate, the number of blow holes significantly reduced or even completely avoided.
In his presentation "blow holes from a technical point of view," he to mark the International Year of Chemistry, he was aware that the laboratory, for which he is responsible, with Polymeren modified Asphalte developing similar to the asphalt mix, but greater mechanical resistance in both high and low temperatures.
Herrera Nájera said that this type of modified Asphalte in areas with extremely hot climate, such as in some cities in the north of the country, should be used to improve the behaviour of the surface and the incidence of blow holes.
He said that the asphalt, the hardest part of oil - a hydrocarbon link, part of which has a high Molekulargewicht - the so-called Asphaltene - and the other part is a low - the so-called Malthene together, they give the effective his typical zähelastisches behavior.
Zähelastisches behaviour of Asphalts means that this is at high temperatures of nearly 180 ° C as a liquid, at 120 ° C, it is very tough liquid and nearly 50 ° C, while he is fragile at very low temperatures.
"This means that the resilience of the Asphalts on the streets is not uniform, but on a day depending on the weather conditions and temperature fluctuations changes," led the chemical engineer.
The researchers the FQ said, the streets of Mexico City had a flexible effective by a majority of six material classes together, of which the last three asphalt.
Among the top layers would wear a layer of asphalt from small, asphalt gebadeten there and then entrenched stones.
Each piece this decay class, whether in asphalt gebadet.
If the vehicles travel and forces that produced this class provides a good forces in the effective distribution.
"If it modified asphalt, would distribute the forces is even better," said the chemical engineer.
"On the wear class," he tells us, "will make a final class, the so-called Tragschicht from tiny stones, i.e. from sand, also in asphalt gebadet.
Since this class in contact with the car tyres, they need greater mechanical power than the wear and it must produce friction.
This effective receives the most forces and distributed the Tragschicht also needs a proper thickness and the material from which it is, must be maintained.
The weather conditions, in particular, humidity and temperature fluctuations, are other important factors to be taken into consideration, above all the water, "he said," because it affects the behaviour of wear class.
If the site is wet, filthy water in the class and is just difficult again. This causes a softening of all sections of the road surface and, as a result, the incidence of blow holes.
If a blow hole occurs, "he said," will begin the deck class City during the wear class only then will be affected, but the damage was not immediately, but it is a process that at the first sign of proper maintenance programmes should be maintained. "
The member of the Sistema Nacional de Investigadores (National Research System of Mexico) said that the vehicle load another important reason for the incidence of blow holes. Therefore the thickness of each class of the surface is in relation to the vehicle weight, and it must be ensured that, in order to prevent frequent blow holes this rule is respected.
Rafael Herrera pointed out that many research in coming, for example, Asphaltemulsionen in other countries are already on the market, and the blow holes simply and without the use of high temperatures could repair.
