This was the work of the doctor, the corpse of Alfonso Cano Identified
A Lophoskopist from Cali, as the man who "Alfonso Cano" identified in history.
The work of these officials plays a key role.
On 4 November was a Lophoskopist of investigative unit of the Public Prosecutor's Office (CTI) from Cali as the man of the identity of the leader of the FARC (Fuerzas Revolucionarias de Colombia Armadas - Revolutionary Armed Forces of Colombia) confirmed: "Alfonso Cano" by comparison of fingerprints.
Of the seven Lophoskopisten in the department of CTI, had Eliazar González call this week, a man from the Puerto Tejada for 21 years in criminal investigations.
At the beginning of his career working in communities of Chocó González, where he often five days in the jungle had to go in order to achieve the place where the bodies were that he should identify.
2000 siedelte after Valle on and after the completion of the necessary courses specialized he Lophoskopie, this is the study of the skin, the friction is evident in the land.
In the week of the use of the so-called Alfonso Cano was Eliazar pointed out, put clothes for at least three days.
Nothing much awaited him.
Friday night, he flew by helicopter from Palmira after Cauca.
He knew he should identify two bodies, and that the suspicion was that the man who led the world's oldest guerrilla, could be, so he should the ten finger-Abdruckblatt of Guillermo León Sáenz (his real name).
But with the Untersuchungste when he reached the place where the body was, he could not identify because of his physical appearance, because this was the images that he had seen in the media, not in the slightest.
He had no beard, was dressed as a pawn of the area, no glasses and was very much thinner.
But fingerprints don't lie.
Armed with a magnifying glass, ink, a lamp and a pocket Pflanzkelle Eliazar compared with the fingerprints of the corpse on the Abdruckblatt.
He had seen right: It was "Alfonso Cano".
This was still the same night originating from Puerto Tejada men responsible for the defence minister, Juan Carlos Pinzón, say that it is the leader of the FARC.
Search for clues
For a Daktyloskopen from Sijín in Cali was the recognition that the President Juan Manuel Santos Eliazar Gonzalez at a press conference on the use of "Cano" paid, very important.
Not many people know our work.
The Daktyloskopie is an exact science without error rate, a key factor in the dissolution of a crime can be.
Lophoskopisten identify not only corpses, they also support investigations into accusations of murder and robbery cases and confirm the identity of the person arrested.
In her arrest many criminals are false identity papers, or they are not.
We are taking the fingerprints and are looking for these in the database.
The researchers told us that he is in a theft of a piece of wall had to pull out of a house, because the thief had precisely at this point with his hand when he was a aufgestützt with jewellery and money full gestopften Safe herauszog.
"Walls are difficult because their surface for fingerprinting are inadequate, but in this case we have the imprint of the whole hands and the offender, who had participated in several thefts, identify," he recalled.
With the help of fingerprints can also be exonerated or murder suspects.
Recently, one death, surrounded by bottles of spirits.
The investigation was suspected that a family member tatverdächtig could be, and indeed was a fingerprint on the bottle.
Although this does not guarantee that the murderer, so it is with the place where the offence was committed in context.
A Daktyloskopist of CTI stated that "the fingerprints with chemical or physical Reagenzen the object."
When they appear, a Pflanzkelle or a band on the carriage.
The prints are then sent to Asif, that is the criminal database, or to Personenstandamt.
"The problem is that there are still many Colombians are undocumented," said the expert from the CTI.
He said that not everything is as it in the TV series presented SCI.
As gold is not all that glitters is not everything it touches turns to a fingerprint.
Nevertheless, it can be used, if you make a comparison.
