GDP is growing by 1.5%, thanks to the domestic consumption and stop the cycle of free fall from the beginning of March
Since the last March was paralyzed Japan's economy, which is still in the recovery after the devastating earthquake that einmündete into a nuclear crisis and the worst disaster that Japan has experienced the second world war.
