Tokyo has entrusted to the domestic market, after the yen, Japan's currency - in one of the "haven currencies" of investors before the debt crisis in the euro zone and the bleak forecasts for the U.S.A., a privilege that as a tombstone in the accounts of the export business.
With a tougher currency are the products more expensive abroad, a serious problem for a country whose economy on the health of the major technology producers.
